<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Active</u>: Uncheck to exclude this opportunity from searches even if 
    it has not yet expired.
</div>
<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Name</u>: Two or three words as if it's a job title.
</div>
<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Description</u>: A few words as if it's a job description. Let prospective volunteers
    know how many hours and days in a week they're needed. Say what kinds of things
    they'll be doing.
</div>
<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Expiration</u>: Unless otherwise provided, the opportunity will expire in 13 weeks. 
    After expiration the opportunity will not appear in any searches.
</div>
<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Minimum age</u>: The minimum age of a volunteer for this opportunity.
</div>
<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Group OK?</u>: Check this box if the opportunity is appropriate for groups.
</div>
<div class=" mb-2">
    <u>Background check req'd?</u>: Check this box if your organization requires a background
    check for volunteers interested in this opportunity.
</div>
